h3 Pills
p.-text Use the <code>-pill</code> modifier class to render badges with a more pronounced border-radius.
h4 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    .a-badge(class=`-pill -m--1`)
      span Badge
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="a-badge -pill">
      <span>Badge</span>
    </div>
