h3 Text Transform
h4 Uppercase
p.-text Use the <code>-text--uppercase</code> text utility class to render badges in all uppercase. <code>-text--lowercase</code> and <code>-text--capitalized</code> are also supported.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    .a-badge(class=`-text--uppercase -m--1`)
      span Badge
  :code(lang="html")
